                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "Obqf6",
                  "name": "Words",
                  "fill": "$text-tertiary",
                  "content": "2,156 字",
                  "fontFamily": "$font-sans",
                  "fontSize": "$text-tiny",
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "aU6Cc",
                  "name": "Spacer",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "height": 1
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "DHzKX",
                  "name": "Loc",
                  "fill": "$text-tertiary",
                  "content": "卷一 · 第 3 章",
                  "fontFamily": "$font-sans",
                  "fontSize": 9,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "iX3iN",
              "name": "Article",
              "clip": true,
              "width": "fill_container",
              "height": "fill_container",
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 10,
              "padding": [
                4,
                2
              ],
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "f8Rfp",
                  "name": "Para",
                  "fill": "$text-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "林川踏入宗门山门的那一刻,便感到一股磅礴的灵气扑面而来,那是一种远胜于凡俗的清冽气息,让他经脉中的真气都不由自主地运转起来。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "fontFamily": "$font-sans",
                  "fontSize": "$text-sm",
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "PUx5d",
                  "name": "Para",
                  "fill": "$text-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "「新晋弟子,皆需先拜祖师堂。」引领他的是一名灰袍中年人,语气淡漠,目光却如同鹰隼般锐利,扫过林川的每一寸神情。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "fontFamily": "$font-sans",
                  "fontSize": "$text-sm",
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "HSCe4",
                  "name": "Para",
                  "fill": "$text-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "林川心中微凛,面上却不动声色,依言随众人走向祖师堂。堂内香烟袅袅,三尊雕像静默矗立,似在俯瞰众生。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "fontFamily": "$font-sans",
                  "fontSize": "$text-sm",
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "NpCtp",
                  "name": "Para",
                  "fill": "$text-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "就在他目光触及雕像的瞬间,丹田内那道沉寂已久的龙脉虚影,竟微微震颤起来……",
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "fontFamily": "$font-sans",
                  "fontSize": "$text-sm",
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "raGBr",
                  "name": "Para",
                  "fill": "$text-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "「嗯?」林川心头一跳,连忙收敛心神。这龙脉虚影自觉醒以来从未有过如此反应,难道这尊雕像,与他的身世有着某种隐秘的关联?",
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "fontFamily": "$font-sans",
                  "fontSize": "$text-sm",
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "nc8yB",
                  "name": "Para",
                  "fill": "$text-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "他不动声色地拜了三拜,随众人退出祖师堂,心中却已暗暗记下了这件事——日后再寻机探究。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "fontFamily": "$font-sans",
                  "fontSize": "$text-sm",
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "vnbZN",
                  "name": "Para",
                  "fill": "$text-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "回到弟子居所,林川闭目凝神,再度探入丹田。那道龙脉虚影安静地盘踞在气海深处,方才的震颤仿佛只是错觉,可他眼底的那一抹疑色,却再也无法散去。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "fontFamily": "$font-sans",
                  "fontSize": "$text-sm",
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
