                      ],
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "m2vOPf",
                          "fill": "$text-primary",
                          "content": "第一章 · 龙脉觉醒",
                          "fontFamily": "$font-sans",
                          "fontSize": "$text-lg",
                          "fontWeight": "600"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "c9Taa",
                          "fill": "$text-body",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "林动站在乌坦城林家演武场中央, 抬头望着漫天星辰。十四岁的他, 本该是族中最耀眼的天才, 如今却被讥讽为「废物」。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.8,
                          "fontFamily": "$font-sans",
                          "fontSize": "$text-md",
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "C5aesb",
                          "fill": "$text-body",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "「修为又退了! 炼气三段都不到。」二哥林震的冷笑从远处传来。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.8,
                          "fontFamily": "$font-sans",
                          "fontSize": "$text-md",
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "J2Ix48",
                          "fill": "$text-body",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "他握紧拳头, 指节发白。父母留下的那枚古朴玉佩, 在他掌心微微发烫 —— 那是他唯一的念想, 也是他从未告诉任何人的秘密。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.8,
                          "fontFamily": "$font-sans",
                          "fontSize": "$text-md",
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "JK5Ar",
                          "fill": "$text-body",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "就在这时, 玉佩中传来一道苍老而威严的声音:「小子, 想变强吗?」",
                          "lineHeight": 1.8,
                          "fontFamily": "$font-sans",
                          "fontSize": "$text-md",
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
